        <body>
            <pb facs="MSVII63v"/>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem" rhyme="aabcbcdcdeaaffgghhiiaajjklklmnmnhhiiaaoop" met= "-+|-+|-+|-+|"> <!--Not sure about form, if "where" is supposed to rhyme with "war" and if the form should be broken by the page break-->
                <head type="title"><space quantity="16" unit="chars" /><placeName corresp="#LAKECOMO">Lago di Como</placeName></head>
                <lg type="stanza" n="1">
                    <l>It was a little peaceful bay<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="lago_di_como_glosses_contextual.php#PEACEFULBAY"/></l>
                    <l>Beneath the precipices grey<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="lago_di_como_glosses_contextual.php#PRECIPICES"/></l>
                    <l>Lay deep, and blue, and calm, but clear,<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">825</add></l>
                    <l>As is the sapphire, and you saw</l>
                    <l>The precipices sharp and sheer</l>
                    <l>And the white clouds careering war</l>
                    <l>And the blue sky and the high hills</l>
                    <l>Neath the cold waters <del rend="strikethrough">as</del> <add place="above"><space quantity="20"></space>where</add> they slept<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">830</add></l>
                    <l>Seemed fed by thousand mountain rills</l>
                    <l>Flowed upward from the crystal depth</l>
                    <l>And all along that quiet bay<ref type="gloss_textual" target="lago_di_como_poem_glosses_textual.php#QUIETBAY" /></l>
                    <l>A range of little shipping lay</l>
                    <l>With their red flags drooped downward right<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">835</add></l>
                    <l>And sheltered by their awnings white</l>
                    <l>From the high suns red scorching look</l>
                    <l>That oer the living waters shook</l>
                    <l>A blaze of hot, and swarthy glow</l>
                    <l>When we had launched from below<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">840</add></l>
                    <l>The shade of the tall cliffs, and came</l>
                    <l>Where <placeName corresp="#LAKECOMO">Como</placeName> rolled his breast of flame</l>
                    <l>Down southward winding far away</l>
                    <l>The olives tints of gentle gray</l>
                    <pb facs="MSVII64r"/>
                    <fw type="pageNum" place="top-right"><handShift new="#HANDWGC" medium="pencil"/>64</fw>
                    <l><handShift new="#HANDJR1833-34" script="script" medium="ink"/>Stooped to his borders from between<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">845</add></l>
                    <l>The hills uncultivated green</l>
                    <l>And orange groves him girded round</l>
                    <l>Blossoming oer him fragrantly</l>
                    <l>And in the sleep of his profound</l>
                    <l>White villages shone silently<ref type="gloss_textual" target="lago_di_como_poem_glosses_textual.php#WHITEVILLAGES" /><add rend="linenumber-right-JR">850</add></l>
                    <l>And from our prow the ripples flash</l>
                    <l>Threw forth its little sparkles paly</l>
                    <l>The light sound of the oars dash</l>
                    <l>Came dancing oer the waters gaily</l>
                    <l>There was blue above, and blue below <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">855</add></l>
                    <l>And the gleam of the eternal snow</l>
                    <l>Forth from the fastnesses it came</l>
                    <l>Of the high <geogName corresp="#ALPS">alps</geogName> retiring <del rend="strikethrough">th</del> chain<ref type="gloss_textual" target="lago_di_como_poem_glosses_textual.php#FASTNESSES" /></l>
                    <l>And all along the shored whereer,</l>
                    <l>The stormwinds wont to chafe the wave <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">860</add></l>
                    <l><subst><add rend="overwriting">The</add><del>A</del></subst> <del rend="strikethrough">crucif</del> crucifix is shrined there</l>
                    <l>That <persName type="scriptural" corresp="#JESUSCHRIST">Christ</persName> may hear the passioned prayer</l>
                    <l>May hear, may <del rend="strikethrough">listen</del><add place="below"><space quantity="16"></space>pity</add>, and may save</l>
                </lg>
                <milestone unit="undeclared" rend="hr-threequarter"/>
            </div>
